!begin_node Cookie, SwTm

(!B)Show Time(!b) - The ultimate informative clock

Runs in all Atari resolutions. Shows the time, free RAM (also with 
MagiC), the date, CapsLock-/DCF status etc.

Hotkeys for clock-switching with Turbo cards or Mega STEs. CapsLock 
LED. With INF file, display and Turbo on/off-switchable, movable.

The cookie points to a data structure with which ShowTime can be 
swiched on/off.

Modifies vectors: (!nolink [GEMDOS])-trap, (!nolink [VDI/AES])-trap, IKBD. 

Copyright status: Freeware/Postcardware.

!end_node

